Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.74,0:00:01.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Darkness and Light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.91,0:00:03.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Into the chaos of\nthe Feudal Era{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.58,0:00:05.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the Sacred Jewel brings a\n{\i1}group of strangers together.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.01,0:00:09.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}500 years across time,\ntheir destinies are controlled{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.08,0:00:11.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}by the few remaining shards\nof the Jewel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.02,0:00:12.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Feudal Fairy Tale:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:15.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We learned that the remaining\NSacred Jewel shard{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}was to be found at the border\nbetween this world and the netherworld.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then Sesshomaru appeared\nbefore us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.53,0:00:24.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What will his father's sword,\NTenseiga, divulge?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.76,0:02:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:07.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As you've guessed,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:09.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I am one of Naraku's\nincarnations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.40,0:02:12.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're {\i1}Naraku's....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.41,0:02:15.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Would you like to search\nfor it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.81,0:02:17.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.54,0:02:18.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sacred Jewel shard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:22.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! I don't give a damn about\nthe next world or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but if there's a shard to be\nfound there,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:27.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,you can go there yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:45.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you.!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.91,0:02:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}This brat... just what is he thinking?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:02:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:11.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- {\i1}Oh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.93,0:03:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I wonder what's going on?\N- {\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I shall go and ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.98,0:03:26.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Miss, will you bear my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:32.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,M-O-N-K!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.49,0:03:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Owwwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:36.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:37.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It was just a greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our village was attacked by\na headless demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:47.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It tore up the {\i1}village....{\i0}\NI was scared out of my wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.40,0:03:51.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you're sure that this\ndemon was headless?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:55.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. It used to be the man-eating demon\nwho lived in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:57.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We don't know who ripped\nits head off,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:00.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but a number of villagers have\nalready been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.75,0:04:01.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.78,0:04:03.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We shall exterminate\nthis demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.08,0:04:08.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You think it's wise to let that\nmonk handle this problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:12.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just earlier, he flirted with our women.\NI don't trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:14.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh well, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, please follow\nthe demon's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.67,0:04:23.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really don't need {\i1}to....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.64,0:04:27.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's pretty obvious\nwhich way he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.37,0:04:28.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:40.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:50.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That {\i1}girl....is{\i0} in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:54.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- I {\i1}must....do{\i0} something!\N- You fool! It's too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.31,0:05:01.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Git outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:02.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.55,0:05:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please! Make him stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.88,0:05:10.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:15.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.95,0:05:16.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's a baby raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:19.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's my father!\NPlease don't hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:21.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Hey raccoon dog!\N- I'm an otter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:22.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:25.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure don't look like\nyou're related!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.33,0:05:27.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! No, that's not my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:29.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't know how you can\nmake a mistake like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.00,0:05:32.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but you can explain after\NI take care of this bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.71,0:05:36.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Iron-Reaver, Soul-Stealer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name is Kanta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:56.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,As you can see, I'm {\i1}a....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:57.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:05:58.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm an otter!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:01.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why did you take on the appearance\nof a human girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.57,0:06:03.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa told me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:04.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He said if I disguise myself\nas a human village girl
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,whenever I leave the mountain,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,some idiot will always\ncome to my rescue.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.81,0:06:10.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father is very shrewd.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:14.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Earlier, you called that\ndemon "father."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:19.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, inside this bundle\nis Pa's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:20.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It happened three days {\i1}ago....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.59,0:06:26.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa and I were catching fish\nin the river.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're fantastic, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.57,0:06:34.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's easy once you get\nthe hang of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:36.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Wanna try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.44,0:06:41.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.21,0:06:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have to be aware\nof the depth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.59,0:06:57.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't have an otter drowning\nin a river.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.39,0:06:59.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Kay, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.16,0:07:06.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then, a white child\nriding a demon horse appeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go and hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:11.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Pa?\N- Just go! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Uh-huh....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.95,0:07:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not from hereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:31.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So, you dodged my first blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.73,0:07:40.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You brat! Don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:44.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This will be more fun\nthan I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanta! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,With that life energy,\nyou'll last awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa's head was carried away\nby the current{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.39,0:08:07.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}and swallowed up\nby a waterfall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Oh {\i1}well....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.26,0:08:12.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The child went away\nafter that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.96,0:08:16.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but by the time I retrieved\NPa's head and returned,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:19.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,his body was nowhere\nto be found!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.94,0:08:22.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Use {\i1}this....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:24.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:28.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So the one hunting down\nall the {\i1}demons....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Has to be Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But for what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:36.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,While in his infant stage,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:39.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hakudoshi killed numerous\nmonks and shrine keepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.82,0:08:42.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,In order to get a glimpse of the\nborder between this world and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.23,0:08:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe he's still trying\nto do the same {\i1}thing....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Using the {\i1}demons....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:51.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:08:54.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He looks into the human heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sounds possible to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.38,0:09:00.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unlike humans, demons\ndon't die easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:04.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So if you find your pa's body and\nstick his head back {\i1}on....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:06.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may not be too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:07.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ohh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.39,0:09:08.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You mean he'll revive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.05,0:09:10.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your father must be\nvery robust.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:14.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's already been three {\i1}days....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And if his body has been\nexterminated, it'll be too late for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.00,0:09:21.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't despair!\NInuyasha will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:25.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha helped me avenge\nmy pa in the past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.97,0:09:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tetsusaiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.68,0:09:38.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is very strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.62,0:09:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:42.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's that strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:44.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's so strong, it makes up\nfor the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:46.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,he's also stupid, childish\nand eccentric.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:48.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I {\i1}see....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:50.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you lost your pa, {\i1}too....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.33,0:09:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's be friends, raccoon dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:09:52.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- No, you're a raccoon dog.\N- I'm a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's over this {\i1}way....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.34,0:10:01.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I sense a terrible\ndemonic aura approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shh! Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.84,0:10:07.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll let them know\nwhere we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.38,0:10:08.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.21,0:10:11.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're asking me\nwhat I'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.65,0:10:14.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:19.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, there are rumors of\nstronger demons being stalked
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:22.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,and decapitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Small fry like you need not worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.30,0:10:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Stronger" demons means\NI, Chokyukai, will be targeted next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:37.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nah... nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.45,0:10:51.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... there he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:14.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Brat! I'll tear you to shreds!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:28.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:31.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:38.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I'm not afraid, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.47,0:11:40.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I may be heartless,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,but I wouldn't pick a fight\nwith a kid like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:45.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How dare a mere {\i1}horse....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Entei's making a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:03.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Probably just some monkeys\nor boars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.63,0:12:07.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By the way, have you seen anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're all basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A world of white mist...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:16.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And those things scattered\nbeneath the mist are...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.56,0:12:31.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master {\i1}Jaken....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.99,0:12:32.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:35.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did Lord Sesshomaru go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.19,0:12:37.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's never talkative\nto begin with...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:43.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But since he failed to defeat\NNaraku at Mt. Hakurei,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}he's been even more silent.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.90,0:12:48.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Still, he could at least tell me\nwhere he's going!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.51,0:12:53.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Jaken, when you sigh,\nhappiness runs away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.38,0:12:55.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.68,0:12:59.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenseiga...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is exciting you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A headless demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:38.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- It's getting away!\N- After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.60,0:13:52.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you catch the scent\nof Kanta's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:55.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I also smell blood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.81,0:14:00.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder if someone\ninjured him?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:02.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Will we make it in time?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:12.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Women and children, go inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.79,0:14:15.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The headless demon may return!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A headless demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.07,0:14:22.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Could it be Kanta's pa?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:23.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:27.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If his body is exterminated,\nhe won't be able to resurrect!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.27,0:14:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:30.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah!\NThe scent isn't far!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.71,0:14:35.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But there's a troublesome guy\nnear Kanta's old man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:40.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:42.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:14:59.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.84,0:15:00.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why's he...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:07.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hang on, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.82,0:15:12.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanta, the head!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.55,0:15:13.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It didn't {\i1}work....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.84,0:15:34.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.51,0:15:35.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kanta....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.91,0:15:40.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.81,0:15:43.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:45.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're just\npassing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.48,0:15:48.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't owe you any\nexplanations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:50.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please wait, Sesshomaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.76,0:15:52.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your {\i1}sword....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:57.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tenseiga is the sword\nthat brings back life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please....{\i0}\NUse {\i1}Tenseiga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.16,0:16:01.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,to bring his father {\i1}back....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This has nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:07.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:38.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C-Can you save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:42.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.87,0:16:44.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.78,0:16:49.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,lf... lf his pa {\i1}dies....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:52.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kanta will be all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:56.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.42,0:16:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:16:59.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.02,0:17:01.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:05.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}But....!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.43,0:17:08.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's useless, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's too {\i1}bad....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.94,0:17:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Sesshomaru isn't the\ntype to come to anyone's aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And besides, that {\i1}Tenseiga....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.54,0:17:21.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,isn't something Sesshomaru\ncan use.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:22.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.28,0:17:26.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Unless its bearer has a caring heart,\NTenseiga cannot be wielded.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.38,0:17:28.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:32.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenseiga is stirring...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:35.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it telling me to save\nthat demon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.06,0:17:36.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.86,0:17:41.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Sesshomaru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.47,0:17:43.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:56.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.55,0:17:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the messengers\nof the afterlife.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.63,0:18:09.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He cut something!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.59,0:18:39.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}P-Pa....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.76,0:18:47.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Pa! Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:01.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so glad for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! I thought I'd never\nbe able to come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.49,0:19:14.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Umm....{\i0} Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.66,0:19:18.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hmm....{\i0} A very strange place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.23,0:19:23.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A world shrouded in white mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:28.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I was flying through this world\nwith only my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:32.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I noticed numerous other\ndemon heads
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.18,0:19:35.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,all with terrible expressions\non their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:39.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Demons who were beheaded\nby Hakudoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And when I dove under the {\i1}mist....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.82,0:19:46.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,there were giant bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:49.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Giant bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.13,0:19:56.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, there was a giant skeleton\nclad in magnificent armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.67,0:20:01.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there were lots of other\nskeletons, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.87,0:20:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess that's the world of\nthe afterlife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.21,0:20:05.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pa....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.48,0:20:08.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Thank you so much\nfor saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.98,0:20:10.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm....Sesshomaru,\nthank-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.25,0:20:18.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:23.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}What was Tenseiga\ntrying to tell me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it telling me to remember?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That it involves that place...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.54,0:20:32.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take care, Shippo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.00,0:20:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm glad it all worked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:40.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's all because of you.\NI'll never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.11,0:20:45.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Me neither.\NBe happy with your pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.69,0:20:51.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:03.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sure! You take care, Pa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:09.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shippo... is remembering\nhis father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.35,0:21:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That place that Kanta's father\n{\i1}saw....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:25.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if Hakudoshi\nalready knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.52,0:21:27.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:29.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But where is this place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.46,0:21:31.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,that's covered in white mist\nand strewn with giant bones?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.56,0:21:35.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I may've been there once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.57,0:21:36.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.20,0:21:37.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you remember something\nabout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.20,0:21:38.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah....{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:44.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Inuyasha is thinking the same thing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.05,0:21:52.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}White mist and giant bones...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:55.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The border between this world\nand the next...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The grave of Inuyasha's father...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.20,0:23:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The Sacred Jewel shard can be found\nby Inuyasha's father's grave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.53,0:23:51.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,at the border between\nthis life and the next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah! He wants me to\nvisit his grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:56.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But the black pearl which is the\nentrance to the grave
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.37,0:23:59.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,has already allowed us entry before\nand fulfilled its purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.48,0:24:00.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Isn't there any other way in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.35,0:24:05.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What? A guy named Hosenki who\ncultivates jewels knows the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:10.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Hosenki and the Last Shard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.42,0:24:12.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get it by force if I have to!
